---
title: Double Herb & Parmesan Chicken Involtini Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! Tonight's challenge is involtini, using techniques borrowed from our Italian brothers and sisters. The humble chicken breast is getting a makeover, first being pounded until tender and even, then wrapped around a flavour-packed filling of garlic, herbs, and lots of Parmesan cheese. Your mouth will water when you cut in to perfectly cooked chicken to reveal a molten, cheesy centre. We're salivating just talking about it!
